snippet.textDisplay: Where WILL Mario go next? Super Mario 64's theme was pure basic platforming levels, Super Mario Sunshine's theme was focused on water in a tropical paradise, and Super Mario Galaxy's theme was the beauty of the cosmos. Land, ocean, space. What else is there? The only thing I can think of is Mario going into a magic jungle where he controls plants or something. Then again, I'm no Miyamoto.
snippet.textOriginal: Where WILL Mario go next?
